title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Feb 3 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Feb 3 2022
description:
LA Mayor Eric Garcetti makes the guys laugh with his ridiculous "I held my breath" excuse for appearing unmasked with people at the NFL championship. Washington, DC bar owner Eric Flannery about the city's closing of his business. Clay & Buck talk to Sen. Josh Hawley (R-MO) talking SCOTUS, Ukraine, China Olympics and more. Clay & Buck talk to Former Navy SEAL sniper and Author Jack Carr - on Syria raid.
